<emphasis bold="true" box="[207,335,368,391]" italics="true" pageId="55" pageNumber="56">Meza meza</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Hewitson" box="[350,530,367,392]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" refString="Hewitson, W. C. (1877) Descriptions of twenty-five species of Hesperidae [Hesperiidae]. Annals and Magazine of Natural History, 19, 76 - 85. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222937708682096" type="journal article" year="1877">Hewitson, 1877</bibRefCitation>
